name: CShit
body:
### Get yor CShit done.
A TypeScript based quick course on Data Structures and Algorithms plus Cracking the Coding Interview problems solutions.

### TDD Data Structures and Algorithms
Test suit based (TDD) way of building all your data structures and get some algorithms done. 
Test provided using MochaJS.

### Why TypeScript
Is JavaScript that looks like Java, CtCi solutions are all Java intimidating code for Boots. Plus I can define interfaces for guidance so people can just worry about implementing.

### Authors and Contributors
This is a project created by @sebabelmar in collaboration of @electricessence.
